race.comment: The babies kick us off. WASABI BARBIE (7) just ran into one better at Mackay on debut and will have derived a stack of benefit from that race day experience. Hoop Fenlon stays on top following that first-up placing and looks the one they all have to run down. SWIFT DRAGON (4) is facing the starter for the first time but looked handy winning a recent Sunny Coast trial and gets the services of Wiggins in the irons. Keep very safe. ROCKY PRINCE (3) has been thereabouts in both trials here and only needs some luck from the wide draw to be playing a role in the outcome. SPORT (5) wasn't too far away when at the races for the first time and will have come on with that run now under the belt. In the mix. GOOD ONE CECIL (1) next in line with the 2kg claim.
